model.name: Immunological Healthy State Model of Sphingolipids with IL-6/IL-17/IL-23 immune axis in L.major infection

body.p: In Healthy State, we demonstrated the controlled expression of sphingolipids and the controlled IL-6,IL-17,IL-23 cytokines signalling via SOCS3 mediated regulation.
